    <h3>Submission tips</h3>
    <p>
        Here's a few useful definitions when submitting events:
    </p>
    <dl>
        <dt>English</dt>
        <dd>
            Please ensure that the description is in English with a translation below if required.
        </dd>
    </dl>
    <dl>
        <dt>Call for Papers</dt>
